snippet.title: Rugby 22 | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready and take to the pitch in Rugby 22 this January! 

Play in the most iconic competitions across the world, with stacked club rosters or take to the world stage, playing as one of the many national teams.

With AI improvements, a new difficulty mode, and more, we can't wait for you to see what Rugby 22 has in store! Rugby 22 is coming to Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, and PC.
